# Access Modes & Volume Modes

## Access modes

| Mode | Code | Meaning |
|---|---|---|
| ReadWriteOnce | **RWO** | one **node** RW — default |
| ReadOnlyMany | ROX | many nodes RO |
| ReadWriteMany | **RWX** | many nodes RW — **NFS/CephFS only**, not EBS/PD |
| ReadWriteOncePod | RWOP | one **Pod** cluster-wide (1.27+) |

> PVC requests modes; the PV must support ≥1.

## The CKA gotcha

> Cloud block = **RWO** → a **Deployment + 1 PVC can't scale past 1 replica** (2nd node can't mount). → **StatefulSet + per-Pod PVCs.**

## Volume modes

- **`Filesystem`** *(default)* — formatted, mounted. **99%.**
- **`Block`** — raw device; app owns the format.
